Run Next JS:
cd next-gql-dogs
yarn dev

Next jS Setup:
- yarn create next-app next-gql-dogs

Apollo Sserver Ssetup:
- yarn add graphql apollo-server-micro

Schema Setup using TypeGraphQL:
- yarn add reflect-metadata type-graphql class-validator

Graphql code generator
yarn add @graphql-codegen/cli @graphql-codegen/typescript -D
yarn add @graphql-codegen/typescript-operations -D
yarn add @graphql-codegen/typescript-graphql-request -D  
yarn add @graphql-codegen/typescript-react-query -D



